Reported-by: Breno Leitao <leitao@debian.org>
Fixes: 9d179b865449 ("blkcg: Fix multiple bugs in blkcg_activate_policy()")
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/ZN0p5_W-Q9mAHBVY@slm.duckdns.org
